{"tid":83261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"福建美食節賣童子尿燜豬蹄　食客讚湯好喝","createTime":"2017-01-16T15:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T04:34:20.000Z","uid":25692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c726e7060a85f7b1182d06568925f54d701326","tid":83261,"uid":25692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170116/mobile/bkncn-20170116102600657-0116_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170116%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20170116102600657-0116_05011_001.html&d=REILfn9PG8J42kYIDykZ0JkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=d21607a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170116/mobile/bkncn-20170116102600657-0116_05011_001.html</a> 轉貼東方日報<br />\n<br />\n睇吓d人食得幾滋味<br />\n福建泉州市上周五舉行美食節，在場有攤販竟出售一道「童子尿燜豬蹄」，趙姓攤販稱，童子尿燜豬蹄必須密封起來，不要讓氣體跑出來，當打開蓋聞到的膻味，就是童子尿的味道，直言用童子尿做出來的豬蹄味道特別好吃。有食客進食後都讚不絕口，不但說豬蹄好吃，還稱讚湯好喝，吸引大批食客在場幫襯。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ifbsmk7q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fifbsmk7q&h=1b1c90fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民熱議，有網民覺得「惡心」，直言「太重口味了！」「無語了，直接喝尿吧！」「難以理解他們說好吃的感覺」；有網民稱，「中國自古就有童子尿，不過我是接受不了」；也有人質疑，「誰知道到底是不是真的童子尿？」&nbsp;"},{"pid":"01488b20bd554df898d04ae49cd4a681e8ee56b6","tid":83261,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"不如食埋屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f813e93f1baf6714853561f92f25c609e13c078a","tid":83261,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81c6fef959570df0174b2d0598352255974ef90c","tid":83261,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"食屎狗"},{"pid":"2da94234fe99ad3cdf785666d070f60811cf48b6","tid":83261,"uid":25692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT